
=  draws on the unique characteristics of three-dimensional printing to construct a license that incorporates enforceable documentation, attribution and copyleft provisions [http://jipel.law.nyu.edu/2013/04/three-dimensional-printing-and-open-source-hardware/]

see also:  [[3D Printing and Open Source Hardware Licensing]]


